Assumption: user is going to be logging in as an admin
On open of the application
if the user is signed in already
    immediately go to the "logged in" screen
otherwise show the normal login screen

The "logged in" screen for admins should have these buttons
    Modify Users
    View Inventory
    Logout

Modify Users
    should take the admin to a page where there will be the following buttons
        add User
        Delete User
        (if time permits, change password)

View Inventory
    Add Item
        Creates a new item if item doesn't already exist
        and gives it the corresponding data provided
    Should be able to search for items
        Should be able to search by category
            Should be able to search by category and with the search function
        Each Item should have the following buttons
            Delete Item
            Change Item Description
            Change Stock
